SIMPLE CALCULATOR WEB APP

A lightweight calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It performs arithmetic operations, addition, substraction, multplication, and division.

==> How To Run The Project
    Open the project folder
    Open the index.html file in any browser
    Start calculating

==> How It Works    
  . Buttons are selected using querySelectorAll().

  . When a user clicks a button, an event listener captures the input.

  . The calculator stores the input as a string and evaluate it when "=" is pressed.

  . The display updates dynamically to show each action and result.



